---
title: UI data sets
css: index.css
---

```{r, echo=FALSE}
library(stringr)
library(kableExtra)
md <- list.files(pattern='*.md', recursive=TRUE) |>
  str_subset('^bin/', negate=TRUE) |>
  str_subset('readme.md', negate=TRUE) |>
  str_extract('.*/(.*)\\.md', 1)
#tab <- data.frame(Name = str_glue('<a href="{md}.html">{md}</a>'))
tab <- data.frame(Name = md)
kbl(tab) |>
  column_spec(1, link=str_glue('{md}.html')) |>
    kable_material_dark()
```
